OL,3,CPeople urged to close windows and
OL,4,Cdoors due to fire near retail park
OL,6,FPeople living in Kemsley are being
OL,7,Fadvised to close windows and doors due
OL,8,Fto smoke coming from a fire at an
OL,9,Findustrial premises in Gas Road,
OL,10,FSittingbourne.
OL,12,FSix fire engines are in attendance and
OL,13,Fcrews wearing breathing apparatus are
OL,14,Fusing hose reel jets and main jets to
OL,15,Fextinguish the flames.
OL,17,FThis is breaking news. More to follow.
